{"tid":2255786,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"騎呢街市唔准女攤販過45歲 疑想提高檔次 趕絕老人擺檔","createTime":"2020-10-23T23:27:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T02:42:36.000Z","uid":130626,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5378688417227ae26d83014f75298f35689f4f72","tid":2255786,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T23:27:51.000Z","msg":"內地經濟遭中美貿易戰與武漢肺炎疫情打擊，仍處於復蘇期，各地政府容許民擺攤做小販維生，但湖北武漢市江岸區一處正在裝修的菜市場，疑因想將舊有攤販趕走，竟張貼新規定，要求場內經營的女攤販不得超過45歲，男攤販則不得超過50歲。網民嘲諷：「奇葩、搞笑、喜劇」，還指做攤販都有年齡歧視，難道以後要着三點式賣菜，吸引顧客？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/SYKVV3Q5IJDK5B4YVCFVY4GMD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FSYKVV3Q5IJDK5B4YVCFVY4GMD4%2F&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vMwCZVYJieBIKSEfzXA%2FSmA%3D&h=2f4ed705\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201024%2FSYKVV3Q5IJDK5B4YVCFVY4GMD4%2F&h=7f8614ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201024/SYKVV3Q5IJDK5B4YVCFVY4GMD4/</a>"},{"pid":"4f6b30fced773059dc30c4da716be526d77202d9","tid":2255786,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T23:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3878a5cd1d0ed62c8affb4f30e715a5ece7265c3","tid":2255786,"uid":232754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T23:34:49.000Z","msg":"係我就唔比過30歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a21dde521baef32240ab7da5309410eb5f087c02","tid":2255786,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3878a5cd1d0ed62c8affb4f30e715a5ece7265c3","tid":2255786,"uid":232754,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T23:34:49.000Z","msg":"係我就唔比過30歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T02:24:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=